query:
SELECT * FROM (SELECT
                    index,
                    transaction_index,
                    address,
                    amount,
                    delegated_stake,
                    num_txs,
                    delegated_restake_earnings,
                    delegated_target_baker_id
                FROM accounts
                WHERE
                    address LIKE $5 || '%'
                    AND index > $1
                    AND index < $2
                ORDER BY
                    (CASE WHEN $4 THEN index END) DESC,
                    (CASE WHEN NOT $4 THEN index END) ASC
                LIMIT $3
                ) ORDER BY index ASC
